rows.label: tlk70000056_04_msg0001
rows.name: I heard my da talking in his sleep.

rows.label: tlk70000056_04_msg0002
rows.name:
He called my ma's name and then
said sorry to her...

rows.label: tlk70000056_04_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm not sure what I should do. Or if I
should do anything at all.

rows.label: tlk70000056_04_msg0004
rows.name:
It sucks. Why do I still have to be a kid?
If I was grown up I'd know what to do.

rows.label: tlk70000056_04_msg0005
rows.name:
If I was a Driver like you guys, I'd
definitely know what to say to make
everything OK...
